            <title>[LU-17602] mdd_rename&apos;s error handling can break namespace</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17602</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
			rc2 = __mdd_index_insert(env, mdd_tpobj, tpobj_fid,
						 mdd_object_type(mdd_tobj),
						 tname, handle);
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;i.e. mdd_rename() can insert tname pointing to own FID.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
